_:N9593e1c500a94483ad5299950f6555aa <http://schema.org/description> "The Legal Ombudsman for England and Wales is appointed by the Office for Legal Complaints to run an independent scheme that resolves complaints about lawyers in a fair and effective way, helping to drive improvements to legal services. The Legal Ombudsman works with the Ministry of Justice ." .
